.. code:: console

   $ ult --help
   usage: ult [-h] [-s] NAME
   
   positional arguments:
     NAME
   
   optional arguments:
     -h, --help    show this help message and exit
     -s, --string  show info about characters in the string

   $ ult -s £
   U+00A3 POUND SIGN
   Text: £
   RFC-1345: Pd
   X11 multi-key input sequences:
     <Multi_key> L -
     <Multi_key> - L
     <Multi_key> l -
     <Multi_key> - l
     <dead_currency> l
   Category: Sc (Currency_Symbol)
   Block: U+0080..U+00FF C1 Controls and Latin-1 Supplement (Latin-1 Supplement)
   See also:
     U+20A4 LIRA SIGN
     U+20BA TURKISH LIRA SIGN
     U+10192 ROMAN SEMUNCIA SIGN

   $ ult BACKSPACE
   U+0008 <control-0008>
   Aliases:
     BACKSPACE (control)
     BS (abbreviation)
   RFC-1345: BS
   Category: Cc (Control)
   Block: U+0000..U+007F C0 Controls and Basic Latin (Basic Latin)

   $ ult U+2603
   U+2603 SNOWMAN
   Text: ☃
   Category: So (Other_Symbol)
   Block: U+2600..U+26FF Miscellaneous Symbols

